text-white\" href=\"https://haroboz.com/votre-experience/book-modele-professionnel/\">Book Modèle Pro</a></li>\n \t<li><a class=\"text-sm text-gray-300 hover:text-white\" href=\"https://haroboz.com/portfolio/temoignages-clients/\">Témoignages</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"font-serif text-lg font-bold mb-4\">Haroboz</div>\n<ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n \t<li><a class=\"text-sm text-gray-300 hover:text-white\" href=\"https://haroboz.com/a-propos/\">À Propos</a></li>\n \t<li><a class=\"text-sm text-gray-300 hover:text-white\" href=\"https://haroboz.com/portfolio/\">Réalisations</a></li>\n \t<li><a class=\"text-sm text-gray-300 hover:text-white\" href=\"https://haroboz.com/contact/\">Contact</a></li>\n \t<li><a class=\"text-sm text-gray-300 hover:text-white\" href=\"https://haroboz.com/mentions-legales/\">Mentions légales</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"border-t border-white/10 mt-10 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4\">\n<p class=\"text-sm text-gray-400\">© 2026 Haroboz — Luc Desbois | Photographe Art Masculin | Marseille, Toulon, Nice, Paris</p>\n\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><i class=\"w-5 h-5\" data-lucide=\"instagram\"></i><a class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-white\" href=\"https://haroboz.com/mentions-legales/\">Mentions légales</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</footer><!-- POPUP -->\n<div id=\"booking-popup\" class=\"fixed inset-0 z-[100] flex items-center justify-center p-4 popup-hidden\">\n<div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-brand/60 backdrop-blur-sm\"></div>\n<div id=\"popup-content\" class=\"relative bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl max-w-lg w-full max-h-[90vh] overflow-y-auto\">\n<div class=\"bg-brand rounded-t-2xl p-6 text-center relative\"><button class=\"absolute top-4 right-4 text-white/70 hover:text-white cursor-pointer\"><i class=\"w-6 h-6\" data-lucide=\"x\"></i></button>\n<h3 class=\"text-xl font-serif text-white font-bold\">Réservez votre séance</h3>\n<p class=\"text-white/70 text-sm mt-1\">Réponse confidentielle sous 24h</p>\n\n</div>\n<form id=\"booking-form\" class=\"p-6\">\n<div class=\"space-y-4\">\n<div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-brand mb-1\">Prénom *</label><input class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl text-brand placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand\" name=\"prenom\" required=\"\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Votre prénom\" /></div>\n<div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-brand mb-1\">Email *</label><input class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl text-brand placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand\" name=\"email\" required=\"\" type=\"email\" placeholder=\"votre@email.com\" /></div>\n<div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-brand mb-1\">Téléphone *</label><input class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl text-brand placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand\" name=\"telephone\" required=\"\" type=\"tel\" placeholder=\"06 XX XX XX XX\" /></div>\n<div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-brand mb-1\">Message</label><textarea class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl text-brand placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand resize-none\" name=\"message\" rows=\"3\" placeholder=\"Parlez-moi de votre projet...\"></textarea></div>\n</div>\n<button class=\"w-full mt-6 bg-brand text-white py-4 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-brand-light shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer\" type=\"submit\"><i class=\"w-5 h-5 mr-2\" data-lucide=\"send\"></i> Envoyer ma demande</button>\n<p class=\"text-center text-xs text-gray-400 mt-3\"><i class=\"w-3 h-3 inline\" data-lucide=\"lock\"></i> 100% confidentiel</p>\n\n</form>\n<div id=\"popup-success\" class=\"hidden p-8 text-center\">\n<div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4\"></div>\n<h3 class=\"text-2xl font-serif text-brand mb-2\">Demande envoyée !</h3>\n<p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-6\">Je vous recontacte sous 24h.</p>\n<button class=\"bg-brand text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-medium hover:bg-brand-light cursor-pointer\">Fermer</button>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"floating-cta\" class=\"fixed bottom-6 right-6 z-50 opacity-0 translate-y-4 transition-all duration-300 pointer-events-none\"><button class=\"relative bg-brand text-white w-14 h-14 md:w-auto md:h-auto md:px-6 md:py-3 rounded-full shadow-2xl hover:bg-brand-light flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer pulse-ring text-brand\"><i class=\"w-6 h-6 md:w-5 md:h-5 md:mr-2\" data-lucide=\"calendar\"></i><span class=\"hidden md:inline font-medium\">Prendre RDV</span></button></div>\n</div>",
